---
// Interactive onboarding guide - standalone page, no sidebar
// memdocs.hebbs.ai/guide/
---
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Get Started with HEBBS</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Index, remember, recall, tune. A step-by-step guide to giving any agent real memory." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-snap-type: y proximity; }
    body {
      background: #0a0a0b;
      color: #d4d4d8;
      font-family: "Inter", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    ::selection { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3); }

    /* ── Stage layout ── */
    .stage {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 80px 24px;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .stage-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* ── Typography ── */
    .stage-num {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #f59e0b;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 44px);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ededef;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    /* ── Terminal ── */
    .terminal {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .terminal-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e20;
    }
    .terminal-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .terminal-dot.r { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.5); }
    .terminal-dot.y { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.5); }
    .terminal-dot.g { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.4); }
    .terminal-title { margin-left: 8px; font-size: 11px; color: #3f3f46; }
    .terminal-body { padding: 20px 24px; overflow-x: auto; }
    .terminal-body pre { white-space: pre; }

    /* Terminal colors */
    .t-prompt { color: #f59e0b; }
    .t-cmd { color: #ededef; }
    .t-flag { color: #67e8f9; }
    .t-str { color: #34d399; }
    .t-out { color: #8a8a8e; }
    .t-num { color: #f59e0b; }
    .t-dim { color: #3f3f46; }
    .t-pass { color: #34d399; }
    .t-fail { color: #f87171; }
    .t-warn { color: #fbbf24; }

    /* ── Recall strategy cards ── */
    .recall-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .recall-card {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .recall-card:hover { border-color: #3f3f46; }
    .recall-card.active { border-color: #f59e0b; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.03); }
    .recall-card .query-label {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .recall-card .query-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #ededef;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .recall-card .query-flags {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #3f3f46;
    }
    .recall-card .query-flags .flag { color: #67e8f9; }
    .recall-result {
      margin-top: 16px;
      display: none;
    }
    .recall-card.active .recall-result { display: block; }

    /* ── Input path tabs ── */
    .path-tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .path-tab {
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      background: transparent;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .path-tab:hover { border-color: #3f3f46; color: #d4d4d8; }
    .path-tab.active { border-color: #f59e0b; color: #f59e0b; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.06); }
    .path-content { display: none; }
    .path-content.active { display: block; }

    /* ── Scorecard ── */
    .scorecard {
      display: grid;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .score-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr 60px 60px;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .score-row.header {
      color: #3f3f46;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .score-row.pass { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.05); }
    .score-row.fail { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.05); }
    .score-row .qnum { color: #3f3f46; }
    .score-row .qtext { color: #8a8a8e; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
    .score-row .before { text-align: right; }
    .score-row .after { text-align: right; }

    /* ── Result banner ── */
    .result-banner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      background: rgba(245,158,11,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.15);
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .result-num {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .result-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .result-arrow { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 24px; }
    .result-desc { flex: 1; font-size: 14px; color: #8a8a8e; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── Vertical cards ── */
    .vertical-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }
    .vertical-card {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .vertical-card:hover { border-color: #f59e0b; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.03); }
    .vertical-card .v-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .vertical-card .v-title {
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ededef;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .vertical-card .v-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── Use-case callouts ── */
    .callouts {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .callout {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .callout strong { color: #d4d4d8; font-weight: 600; }

    /* ── Navigation bar ── */
    .guide-nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 200;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 11, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e20;
    }
    .guide-nav a {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .guide-nav a:hover { color: #d4d4d8; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
    .guide-nav a.active { color: #f59e0b; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.08); }
    .guide-nav .nav-back {
      color: #3f3f46;
      margin-right: 12px;
      padding-right: 16px;
      border-right: 1px solid #1e1e20;
    }
    .guide-nav .nav-back:hover { color: #8a8a8e; }

    /* ── Navigation dots ── */
    .nav-dots {
      position: fixed;
      right: 24px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #1e1e20;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .nav-dot.active { background: #f59e0b; transform: scale(1.3); }
    .nav-dot:hover { background: #3f3f46; }

    /* ── Copy button ── */
    .copy-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      right: 12px;
      background: #1e1e20;
      border: 1px solid #3f3f46;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .copy-btn:hover { color: #ededef; border-color: #8a8a8e; }

    /* ── Folder tree ── */
    .folder-tree {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .folder-tree .dir { color: #67e8f9; }
    .folder-tree .file { color: #8a8a8e; }
    .folder-tree .comment { color: #3f3f46; }
    .folder-tree .entity-tag { color: #f59e0b; }

    /* ── Rules file preview ── */
    .rules-file {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .rules-file-header {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #3f3f46;
    }
    .rules-file-body {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #8a8a8e;
    }
    .rules-file-body .heading { color: #f59e0b; font-weight: 600; }
    .rules-file-body .rule { color: #d4d4d8; }

    /* ── Hero section ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
    }
    .hero canvas {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }
    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(36px, 7vw, 64px);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ededef;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero h1 .accent { color: #f59e0b; }
    .hero .hero-sub {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .hero .scroll-hint {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 40px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #3f3f46;
      animation: pulse-down 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse-down {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
      50% { opacity: 0.8; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(6px); }
    }

    /* ── Horizontal timeline ── */
    .timeline {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      margin-top: 28px;
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      left: 24px;
      right: 24px;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f59e0b 0%, #67e8f9 50%, #34d399 100%);
      opacity: 0.25;
    }
    .timeline-item {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 160px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      padding: 0 8px;
    }
    .timeline-dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #f59e0b;
      margin: 14px auto 14px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
    }
    .timeline-item:nth-child(2) .timeline-dot { background: #67e8f9; box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.4); }
    .timeline-item:nth-child(3) .timeline-dot { background: #34d399; box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.4); }
    .timeline-label {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .timeline-label strong { color: #ededef; display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }

    /* ── Terminal typing animation ── */
    .terminal.typing .terminal-body pre {
      visibility: hidden;
    }
    .terminal.typing .terminal-body pre.typed {
      visibility: visible;
    }
    .terminal .cursor {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 8px;
      height: 14px;
      background: #f59e0b;
      margin-left: 2px;
      animation: blink-cursor 0.8s step-end infinite;
      vertical-align: text-bottom;
    }
    @keyframes blink-cursor {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0; }
    }

    /* ── Fade-in animation ── */
    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease-out, transform 0.7s ease-out;
    }
    .fade-up.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .cta-primary { background: #f59e0b; color: #0a0a0b; }
    .cta-primary:hover { background: #fbbf24; }
    .cta-secondary { border: 1px solid #1e1e20; color: #8a8a8e; }
    .cta-secondary:hover { border-color: #3f3f46; color: #d4d4d8; }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .stage { padding: 80px 16px 60px; }
      .terminal-body { padding: 16px; font-size: 11px; }
      .result-banner { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; }
      .nav-dots { display: none; }
      .score-row { grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr 48px 48px; font-size: 10px; }
      .vertical-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .callouts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .guide-nav { overflow-x: auto; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ── Top navigation ── -->
  <nav class="guide-nav">
    <a href="/" class="nav-back">&larr; docs</a>
    <a href="/guide/" class="active">Guide</a>
    <a href="/guide/crm">CRM</a>
    <a href="/guide/legal">Legal</a>
    <a href="/guide/finance">Finance</a>
    <a href="/guide/support">Support</a>
    <a href="/guide/coding">Coding</a>
  </nav>

  <nav class="nav-dots" id="nav-dots">
    <button class="nav-dot active" data-stage="hero" title="Home"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="0" title="Index"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="1" title="Remember"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="2" title="Prime"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="3" title="Recall"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="4" title="Contradictions"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="5" title="Insights"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="6" title="Tune"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="7" title="Start"></button>
  </nav>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- HERO: Bioluminescent graph                                      -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <canvas id="hero-graph"></canvas>
    <div class="hero-content fade-up">
      <h1>Give your agent<br/><span class="accent">real memory.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Not vector search. Not RAG. Temporal reasoning, causal chains, and insights that compound &mdash; in one binary.</p>
      <a href="#stage-0" class="cta-btn cta-primary" style="margin-right: 12px;">Start the guide</a>
      <a href="#stage-7" class="cta-btn cta-secondary">Pick a use case</a>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-hint">&darr; scroll</div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- STAGE 1: Index Your Knowledge                                   -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="stage" id="stage-0">
    <div class="stage-inner fade-up">
      <div class="stage-num">Step 1</div>
      <h2>Index your knowledge</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Organize your workspace. Files inside <code style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #67e8f9;">entities/</code> are automatically scoped. Everything else is shared knowledge any query can surface.</p>

      <div class="folder-tree">
        <pre><span class="dir">workspace/</span>
<span class="dir">  entities/</span>                      <span class="comment">&larr; auto-tagged by subfolder</span>
<span class="dir">    acme-corp/</span>
<span class="file">      call-2026-03-15.md</span>        <span class="entity-tag">&rarr; entity_id: "acme-corp"</span>
<span class="file">      call-2026-03-22.md</span>        <span class="entity-tag">&rarr; entity_id: "acme-corp"</span>
<span class="dir">    project-alpha/</span>
<span class="file">      status-update.md</span>          <span class="entity-tag">&rarr; entity_id: "project-alpha"</span>
<span class="dir">  docs/</span>                          <span class="comment">&larr; shared knowledge, no entity</span>
<span class="dir">  case-studies/</span>
<span class="dir">  playbooks/</span></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="terminal" data-typing style="margin-top: 20px; position: relative;">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <span class="terminal-dot r"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot y"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot g"></span>
          <span class="terminal-title">terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <pre><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs index</span>

<span class="t-out">  Scanning 74 files...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Extracting propositions (10 parallel)...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Detected 3 entities: acme-corp, project-alpha, case-smith-v-jones</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedded 1,284 memories (4.1s)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  &#10003; 74 files &middot; 612 sections &middot; 672 propositions &middot; 3 entities</span></pre>
        </div>
        <button class="copy-btn" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('hebbs index')">copy</button>
      </div>

      <div class="callouts">
        <div class="callout"><strong>CRM:</strong> Product docs, case studies, blogs as shared. Deal folders per account in entities/.</div>
        <div class="callout"><strong>Legal:</strong> Statutes, precedents as shared. Case folders per client in entities/.</div>
        <div class="callout"><strong>Coding:</strong> Architecture docs, ADRs as shared. Project folders in entities/.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- STAGE 2: Remember Everything                                    -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="stage" id="stage-1">
    <div class="stage-inner fade-up">
      <div class="stage-num">Step 2</div>
      <h2>Remember everything</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Three ways to get data in. All produce the same memories. Pick what fits your workflow.</p>

      <div class="path-tabs" id="path-tabs">
        <button class="path-tab active" data-path="files">Files</button>
        <button class="path-tab" data-path="cli">CLI</button>
        <button class="path-tab" data-path="sdk">SDK</button>
      </div>

      <div class="path-content active" data-path="files">
        <div class="terminal">
          <div class="terminal-bar">
            <span class="terminal-dot r"></span>
            <span class="terminal-dot y"></span>
            <span class="terminal-dot g"></span>
